column5: fished the bay on nov 12&13 trolled all day on friday o fish cought on sat we fished a 75 person tourney again o fish cought only 9 fish were weighed in after the tourney we over to shermans point and jiged up 6 eyes for dinner we marked fish both days but the big girls had lock jaw
Sounds like a tough time getting some eyes to commit Corvy At least you were able to nail a few for the pan   good on you Thanks for sharing Leechman
Yes, the fishng was tough - hard to come by,but they're there.  Cheers - Saw the OFC hat on Saturday. Didn't get to say Hi!
doesn't sound good for next weekend the fishing might pick up but the winds are really going to pickup and the temps drop
